      .post-info
        h4.published-info Posted 02/12/2015
        a.btn.btn-info.btn-large.read-it-button(href='http://creativedrewy.blogspot.com/2015/02/wearss-internet-coverage.html', target='_blank') Read It!
        .post-main-content
          div
            | WeaRSS has been getting some coverage on the internet; both on the web and in the land of Android apps. I thought I would share the love.
            br
            br
            | First - and I'm most excited about this - WeaRSS is currently a featured app in the Android Wear section of the Google Play Store! I shared the photo on my 
            a(href='http://instagram.com/creativedrewy', target='_blank') Instagram
            |  profile:
            br
            br
            table.tr-caption-container(align='center', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0', style='margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;')
              tbody
                tr
                  td(style='text-align: center;')
                    a(href='http://photos-a.ak.instagram.com/hphotos-ak-xaf1/t51.2885-15/10949014_1534217380178816_1103921584_n.jpg', imageanchor='1', style='margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;')
                      img(border='0', src='http://photos-a.ak.instagram.com/hphotos-ak-xaf1/t51.2885-15/10949014_1534217380178816_1103921584_n.jpg', height='320', width='320')
                tr
                  td.tr-caption(style='text-align: center;') I never thought this would happen!
            br
            | To see it for yourself open up the Play Store on your Android device (and you 
            i
              b do
            |  have an Android device, right?) and head to the Android Wear page; these are "Hand-Picked for Wear" apps. Swipe down the page and you'll see it listed right there! It's definitely an honor to get recognition from Google in this fashion.
            br
            br
            | WeaRSS has also been getting some video recognition on YouTube. Here is a great video review:
            br
            br
