              iframe.YOUTUBE-iframe-video(allowfullscreen='', data-thumbnail-src='https://ytimg.googleusercontent.com/vi/28ZgrZ77Low/0.jpg', frameborder='0', height='266', src='http://www.youtube.com/embed/28ZgrZ77Low?feature=player_embedded', width='320')
            div(style='clear: both; text-align: left;')
              br
              | And YouTube channel 
              a(href='http://www.youtube.com/channel/UCcRlebYC40o-krbjU8cMC6A', target='_blank') HonestTech
              |  includes it as one of their "5 Must Have Android Wear Apps:"
            div(style='clear: both; text-align: left;')
              br
            .separator(style='clear: both; text-align: center;')
            .separator(style='clear: both; text-align: center;')
              iframe.YOUTUBE-iframe-video(allowfullscreen='', data-thumbnail-src='https://ytimg.googleusercontent.com/vi/3sDHmWVhsHA/0.jpg', frameborder='0', height='266', src='http://www.youtube.com/embed/3sDHmWVhsHA?feature=player_embedded', width='320')
            div(style='clear: both; text-align: center;')
              br
            div(style='clear: both; text-align: left;')
              | A big thanks to the creators of those videos for the coverage. And while you're watching the videos, why don't you give those channels a like or subscribe?
            div(style='clear: both; text-align: left;')
              br
              | The app has been picked up by a couple of websites too:
              br
              ul
                li
                  a(href='http://www.androidwearapps.org/2014/11/wearss-rss-feed-for-android-wear-watch.html#.VN1glC6RUZz', target='_blank') Best Android Wear Apps
                  |  posted an article about it highlighting its features.
                li
                  | Over on 
                  a(href='http://makeuseof.com/', target='_blank') makeuseof.com
                  | , author Ben Stegner included it in his "
                  a(href='http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/6-awesome-apps-android-wear-smartwatch/', target='_blank') 6 More Awesome Apps For Your Android Wear Smartwatch
                  | " list.
            div(style='clear: both; text-align: left;')
              br
              | On a final note, I realize it's not entirely clear how to actually pronounce 'WeaRSS' when you say it out loud. I'll try to lay the confusion to rest: the way I say it is "wear-R-ess-ess;" kind of in a flowing manner. I do pronounce both 'Wear' and 'RSS' but I mash them together a little bit with an extra "R" sound to bridge the two parts together.
            div(style='clear: both; text-align: left;')
              br
            div(style='clear: both; text-align: left;')
              | Naturally, this should help you as you discuss this app with your friends and/or make a positive video review. Right? Right.
            div(style='clear: both; text-align: left;')
              br
